?                                                                            ?
?  1st December 1999.                                                        ?
?                                                                            ?
?  Today we changed back to our original name Addicted To Music (ATM).       ?
?  The channel will be +k and our sitebots/members/friends will from now on  ?
?  be in our private channel.                                                ?
?  We changed back to ATM due the Millenium change and for security reasons. ?
?  ATM also wanna welcome SeRiAlKiLLaH as Leader and Snikerac as Council.    ?
?                                                                            ?
?  We would like to take a moment of your time to introduce ourselves.       ?
?  ATM is a gathering of like minds wishing to bring Quality Mp3             ?
?  releases to the scene in a timely and orderly fashion.                    ?
?                                                                            ?
?  What are we going to stand for?                                           ?
?  We are going to stand for top quality releases and we are going to        ?
?  release all kind of music that hasn&#039;t been released before.               ?
?                                                                            ?
?  We also want to welcome our new members to the ATM family, may the        ?
?  releases and our friendship be with you, guys!.                           ?
?                                                                            ?
?  ATM are currently looking for:                                            ?
?  Rippers, Pre Release & Tuesday Ripper (Must be cable+), T3 Siteops.       ?
